### ================================================================================
### 📤 文件上传模块接口测试
### ================================================================================
### 功能：图片上传、文件管理、URL生成等
### 依赖：需要用户Token，需要配置OSS服务
### 权限：登录用户
### OSS配置：aliyuncs.com endpoint
### ================================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@merchantToken = {{merchantToken}}

### ================================================================================
### 🖼️ 图片上传
### ================================================================================

### 1.1 上传商品图片（multipart/form-data）
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="product-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/product.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data) {
            client.log("✅ 图片上传成功");
            client.log("🔗 图片URL: " + body.data.imageUrl);
            client.log("📁 文件名: " + body.data.filename);
            client.log("📏 文件大小: " + body.data.fileSize);
            client.log("🕐 上传时间: " + body.data.uploadTime);
        }
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 图片上传失败: " + response.body);
    }
%}

### 1.2 上传PNG格式图片
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="product-image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-images/product.png
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ PNG图片上传成功");
    }
%}

### 1.3 上传多张图片（批量上传）
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/images
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="image1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/image1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="image2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/image2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="image3.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/image3.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data && Array.isArray(body.data)) {
            client.log("✅ 批量上传成功");
            client.log("📊 上传数量: " + body.data.length);
            body.data.forEach(function(image) {
                client.log("🔗 " + image.imageUrl);
            });
        }
    }
%}

### 1.4 错误测试 - 上传非图片文件
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 400) {
        client.log("✅ 文件类型验证正常 - 只允许图片");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 文件类型验证异常");
    }
%}

### 1.5 错误测试 - 文件过大
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="large-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/large-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 400) {
        client.log("✅ 文件大小验证正常 - 超过限制");
    } else {
        client.log("⚠️ 文件大小验证需要检查");
    }
%}

### 1.6 错误测试 - 未登录上传
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/test.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 401) {
        client.log("✅ 未登录上传验证正常");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 未登录上传验证异常");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 🔗 URL生成和验证
### ================================================================================

### 2.1 生成上传URL（用于前端直传OSS）
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/generate-url
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "product-image.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileSize": 1024000
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data) {
            client.log("✅ 生成上传URL成功");
            client.log("🔗 上传URL: " + body.data.uploadUrl);
            client.log("🔗 访问URL: " + body.data.accessUrl);
            client.log("🕐 过期时间: " + body.data.expiration);
            client.log("🔑 签名: " + body.data.signature);
        }
    }
%}

### 2.2 验证图片URL有效性
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/validate-url
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://oss-example.com/products/image.jpg"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data) {
            client.log("✅ URL验证成功");
            client.log("✅ URL有效: " + body.data.valid);
            client.log("📏 文件大小: " + body.data.fileSize);
            client.log("🕐 存在时间: " + body.data.age);
        }
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 🗑️ 文件删除
### ================================================================================

### 3.1 删除已上传图片
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://oss-example.com/products/image-to-delete.jpg"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 图片删除成功");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 图片删除失败");
    }
%}

### 3.2 批量删除图片
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/images
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrls": [
    "https://oss-example.com/products/image1.jpg",
    "https://oss-example.com/products/image2.jpg",
    "https://oss-example.com/products/image3.jpg"
  ]
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 批量删除成功");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 📊 文件管理
### ================================================================================

### 4.1 查询用户上传的文件列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/files

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data && Array.isArray(body.data)) {
            client.log("✅ 查询文件列表成功");
            client.log("📊 文件数量: " + body.data.length);
            body.data.forEach(function(file) {
                client.log("📁 " + file.filename + " - " + file.fileSize);
            });
        }
    }
%}

### 4.2 按类型查询文件
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/files?type=image

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 按类型查询文件成功");
    }
%}

### 4.3 按时间范围查询文件
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/files?startDate=2026-06-01&endDate=2026-06-30

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 按时间查询文件成功");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 🎨 图片处理
### ================================================================================

### 5.1 获取图片缩略图URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/thumbnail?url=https://oss-example.com/products/image.jpg&size=200x200

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data) {
            client.log("✅ 获取缩略图URL成功");
            client.log("🔗 缩略图URL: " + body.data.thumbnailUrl);
        }
    }
%}

### 5.2 获取不同尺寸的图片
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/resize?url=https://oss-example.com/products/image.jpg&width=800&height=600

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 获取调整尺寸URL成功");
    }
%}

### 5.3 图片裁剪
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/crop?url=https://oss-example.com/products/image.jpg&x=10&y=10&width=200&height=200

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 获取裁剪URL成功");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 🔒 安全和权限测试
### ================================================================================

### 6.1 测试未授权访问他人文件
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/files?userId=999

> {%
    if (response.status === 403) {
        client.log("✅ 文件访问权限验证正常");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 文件访问权限验证异常");
    }
%}

### 6.2 测试删除他人文件
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://oss-example.com/merchant-files/image.jpg"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 403) {
        client.log("✅ 文件删除权限验证正常");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 文件删除权限验证异常");
    }
%}

### 6.3 测试URL注入攻击
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/validate-url
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://evil.com/malicious.jpg"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 400 || response.status === 403) {
        client.log("✅ URL安全验证正常");
    } else {
        client.log("⚠️ URL安全验证需要加强");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 📈 存储统计
### ================================================================================

### 7.1 获取用户存储统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/storage/statistics

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data) {
            client.log("✅ 获取存储统计成功");
            client.log("📊 文件数量: " + body.data.fileCount);
            client.log("💾 总大小: " + body.data.totalSize);
            client.log("📊 图片数量: " + body.data.imageCount);
            client.log("📊 其他文件: " + body.data.otherCount);
        }
    }
%}

### 7.2 获取平台存储统计（管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/storage/platform-statistics

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 获取平台存储统计成功");
    } else if (response.status === 403) {
        client.log("⚠️ 需要管理员权限");
    }
%}

### ================================================================================
### 💡 测试注意事项
### ================================================================================

### 1. 文件上传需要配置OSS服务，确保OSS配置正确
### 2. 图片文件大小有限制，通常最大5-10MB
### 3. 支持的图片格式：jpg, jpeg, png, gif, webp
### 4. 文件上传可能较慢，注意设置合理的超时时间
### 5. 删除文件是永久操作，谨慎测试
### 6. URL生成和验证需要OSS签名机制支持
### 7. 图片处理功能依赖OSS图片处理服务

### ================================================================================
### 🛠️ 环境准备
### ================================================================================

### 准备测试图片文件：
### 1. 创建 test-images 目录
### 2. 放入几个测试图片（product.jpg, product.png等）
### 3. 确保图片大小在限制范围内

### OSS配置检查：
### 1. 检查 application-dev.yml 中的OSS配置
### 2. 确认 accessKeyId 和 accessKeySecret 正确
### 3. 确认 bucket 和 endpoint 配置正确
### 4. 确认 bucket 权限允许上传

### ================================================================================
### 📋 完整上传流程
### ================================================================================

### 标准上传流程：
### 1. 用户选择图片文件
### 2. 前端生成上传URL（或直接上传到服务器）
### 3. 上传图片到OSS
### 4. 获取图片URL
### 5. 将URL关联到商品或订单
### 6. 可以生成缩略图用于列表显示

### 批量上传流程：
### 1. 用户选择多张图片
### 2. 批量上传到OSS
### 3. 获取所有图片URL
### 4. 将第一张设为主图
### 5. 保存到商品图片列表

### ================================================================================